If Opps overcall  2@C  over 1NT, then you ONLY have a FAST cue-bid available,  because after   2NT  -  3@C  
the only  @c  bid below 3NT has been taken by that very sequence.

In these circumstances the FAST cue says NOTHING about the presence or absence of a Club stop but just shows interest in the Majors.

